Scene ID: SC_001_008
Allowed events: Vane's introduction, Aura of Intimidation effect, discovery of Artie's anomaly status, formal duel challenge, Artie's escape.
Forbidden milestones: none (milestone: vane_rivalry_started = NOT_YET)

